extraDescription: Under the direction and leadership of the Director, EI Program Management Office (EI-PMO), and the Sr. PwC Project Manager, this Professional Services resource will support the ongoing development and enhancement of the business analysis discipline within the EI-PMO.  This may include assignment to a specific project or projects, and/or assignment to activities in support of the EI PMO. The assigned resource shall provide business analysis and support to the EI PMO as it relates to needs of the assigned EI Transformation projects.
